g","title":"Seafood and corn chowder","publishedAt":"2018-07-30T00:00:00Z","nutrition":{"protein":"19.6 g","fat":"15.3 g","uom":"per 1 portion","carbohydrates":"18.1 g","calories":"1442.8 kJ \/ 343.5 kcal"},"usefulItems":"bowl","hintsAndTricks":["<strong>Fish chowder:<\/strong> Replace the seafood marinara mix with 500 g firm white fish, salmon or haddock, cut into pieces (4-5 cm).","You can replace the dry sherry with Pernod.","For more texture (and protein), add hard-boiled eggs, cut into quarters, to soup just before serving.","Please refer to <i>The Basic Cookbook<\/i> or the <i>Everyday Cookbook<\/i> for the Chicken stock paste recipe."],"basicInfo":["easy","20m","40m","6 portions"]}